<scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
<p>This collection includes individual carte-de-visite portraits of Civil War soldiers that are not part of any manuscript collection.  It also includes a few group portraits.</p>
     
<p>Many other Civil War portraits are found in individual manuscript collections.  To find a listing of collections containing portraits and other photographs from the Civil War, please refer to the MIRLYN catalog under the subject United States--History--Civil War, 1861-1865.</p>

</scopecontent>

